Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.20,0:22:24.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あまたの功を上げた者だけが\N達せられる場所です
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.78,0:22:28.63,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,As a result, gaining the title of full general
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.80,0:22:28.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結果 将軍が手にするのは―
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.63,0:22:34.63,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,is the immense honor of being responsible for and controlling thousands and tens of thousands of lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.67,0:22:34.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,千 万の人間の命を束ね戦う責任と\N絶大な栄誉
